    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction to blueprint-compiler</title>

      <para>
        The <application>blueprint-compiler</application> package contains a
        compiler for a markup language for GTK user interfaces. This is mostly
        used with GNOME applications at the moment.
      </para>

      &lfs130_checked;

      <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Package Information</bridgehead>
